      NonDeterministicParser ParserService.getTransitionBasedGlobalLearningParser(FeatureWeightVector featureWeightVector, ParsingConstrainer parsingConstrainer, Set<ParseConfigurationFeature<?>> parseFeatures, int beamWidth)
      A non-deterministic parser implementing transition based parsing, using a Shift-Reduce algorithm, but applying global learning.
      The features are thus used to rank parse configurations after all valid transitions have been applied, rather than being used to select the next transition for an existing configuration.
      com.joliciel.talismane.parser.TransitionBasedGlobalLearningParser ParserServiceImpl.getTransitionBasedGlobalLearningParser(FeatureWeightVector featureWeightVector, ParsingConstrainer parsingConstrainer, Set<ParseConfigurationFeature<?>> parseFeatures, int beamWidth)

      A non-deterministic parser implementing transition based parsing, using a Shift-Reduce algorithm.
      See Nivre 2008 for details on the algorithm for the deterministic case.
